{
  "text": "Advances in nanomaterials technology, and particularly in carbon nanotube technology [CITATION_1] , are enabling the sensitizing and charging of nanoparticles to make them attracted to electromagnetic sources, and specifically with centrosome clusters.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "8889742"
